items.title: Cubs showing champion form again
items.summary: Amid all the focus on the Indians, Dodgers and Astros, the defending World Series champs have quietly turned their season around.
items.content: Amid all the focus on the Indians, Dodgers and Astros, the defending World Series champs have quietly turned their season around.

items.title: Nats 'very confident' with Strasburg in top form
items.summary: If the Dodgers and Nationals meet again next month - and barring something very odd during the next two weeks, that wouldn't happen until the NLCS - Washington has a reason to believe it won't be doomed to repeat a similar fate after losing Game 5 of the NLDS at home. His name is Stephen Strasburg.

items.title: Wisdom slugs Triple-A Memphis to Pacific Coast League crown
items.summary: Patrick Wisdom hit a career-high 31 homers this season, but Sunday night's blast may be the most memorable as it helped lift Triple-A Memphis to a Pacific Coast League championship.
